- Update TF to 2.6.0
- Update Eigen to latest commit https://gitlab.com/libeigen/eigen/-/commit/82dd3710dac619448f50331c1d6a35da673f764a (version 3.4.90)
  -  I added the cms changes ( https://github.com/cms-externals/eigen-git-mirror/commit/5c78a3657102009ea20604808bf4d5a30df6ec7a ) needed for powerpc and cuda/GPU. Few of our changes were rejected. Rejected changes are available here https://muzaffar.web.cern.ch/muzaffar/eigen-82dd3710dac619448f50331c1d6a35da673f764a.rej , @fwyzard @ericcano can you please check if these are needed and open a PR for cms-externals/eigen-git-mirror branch  cms/master/82dd3710dac619448f50331c1d6a35da673f764a ?
